DETAILED DRAWINGS AND MATERIALS (DETAILS): The following details including product details, material, colour, finish and scale drawings (elevations at 1:20 and sections/details at 1:5) showing the proposed window/door and masonry surround at 1:20 as appropriate in plan and elevation shall be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority prior to the relevant works commencing:

(A)     window at lower ground floor lightwell;
